\begin_layout Standard
Due to imposed magnetic field 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 the impulse operator on the ring has an adjustment:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{p}=\frac{1}{i}\frac{d}{dx}\pm\Phi$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi=\frac{\pi r^{2}B}{\Phi_{0}}$
\end_inset

, 
